{"tid":1536914,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無組織、議員或任何公會可以出封信比警務處","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T02:29:41.000Z","uid":36994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1bb529da3b10f49f132dce5717fa158f62965e","tid":1536914,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"黑警濫權、講大話呃香港人<br />\n包庇同袍、有意圖借拘捕使用過份武力<br />\n意圖謀殺香港人及示威者<br />\n<br />\n人在做，天在看<br />\n<br />\n我真係覺得紙永遠真係包唔著火<br />\n好希望有組織、議會或任何公會可以出封信譴責警方<br />\n<br />\n有曬影片，有曬證據都仲要狡辯<br />\n好想話比你地班柒頭知，當差唔係惡曬<br />\n<br />\n如果你地繼續咁樣，唔好怪香港人行動進一步升級<br />\n升級既程度難以想像，亦無人預知到情況有幾惡劣<br />\n<br />\n講真，如果你地係mon post狗，你地心知肚明啦！<br />\n不如你真係搵日收工諗下香港發生咩事。<br />\n你日日番工洗曬腦，黑白不分，顛倒是非。<br />\n如果你地無做錯，所有人都會專重你，但依家？<br />\n<br />\n我明你養家活兒，但依場運動邊個贏邊個輸都好，<br />\n黑警永遠係黑警，你一世就係咁樣過。<br />\n到時警務處為左保住自己個政治牌坊，<br />\n清算番你地轉頭，你地到時個個精神病入曬青山。<br />\n<br />\n最後講多個，依家佛家已經著緊火，<br />\n你再唔收手，後果真係自己諗掂佢<br />\n到時何君堯議會送曬你地番大陸，<br />\n問心，你真係想咩？<br />\n<br />\n你係政府既警察，其實個職位等同一間茶記既外賣仔；<br />\n老闆係為錢為做生意，唔會同你講人情，<br />\n你成為左阻礙就會踢走你，點都好，做人做狗自己諗！"},{"pid":"d93a84e6bff4973a1325b6fe147ef79abe8f811a","tid":1536914,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34846c588b9784f39ba4d0a01592694767d23ae2","tid":1536914,"uid":212819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"［超長文］前線革命宣言：830隻狗係我地斬嘅<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agmuFrU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agmuFrU</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打們唔洗絕望<br />\n依個方向就正確"},{"pid":"014b60692efedfafc583ea8386ea6cafd2bb89f0","tid":1536914,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccae598a8ce35b52262a95d7028d95a5560066af","tid":1536914,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6etjqh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6etjqh.jpg&h=8d93e192&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79ac9d3cf2c5f3bd785241dbad4fde684eae63fb","tid":1536914,"uid":36994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 